official_title: A joint resolution to provide for a temporary increase in the public debt limit.

summary.text: (Measure passed Senate, roll call #354 (50-41)) Increases the temporary public debt limit set forth in the Second Liberty Bond Act from $400,000,000,000 to $1,290,200,000,000 for FY 1983.

titles.title: A joint resolution to provide for a temporary increase in the public debt limit.
